{"tid":1051973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大圍車房命案】控方決定撤誤殺罪 三被告當庭釋放","createTime":"2019-03-08T04:05:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T04:34:00.000Z","uid":37661,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"940bf27d2aeeabb813b610cf7eb4852239fa95e7","tid":1051973,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:05:32.000Z","msg":"【大圍車房命案】控方決定撤誤殺罪 三被告當庭釋放<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190308/large/1552016425_670b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190308%2Flarge%2F1552016425_670b.jpg&h=5187c138&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首被告陳穗豪（左三）及次被告陳宗達(左二)離庭時有家屬持碌柚葉替他們「洗衰運」。（李潤芳攝 ）(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n沙田大圍去年11月發生命案，多名男子疑走到大圍一間車房進行刑事毀壞，扑爛車房內的GTR跑車，其中一人逃走時被包括車房東主在內的三人追截制服，男子及後死亡。三人原被控一項誤殺罪，但案件經多次提訊後，控方今向法庭透露，在取得死者的驗屍報告後決定對三人撤控。三名被告得悉後即時面露笑容，向到庭旁聽的眾多親友高舉姆指。<br />\n<br />\n三名被告依次為涉事車房的東主陳穗豪（40歲）、附近車房東主陳宗達（32歲）和附近車房職員鄭智斌（29歲），控罪指他們於2018年11月16日在香港新界沙田大圍成運路非法殺死何善恆（42歲）。其中次被告及第三被告申請訟費獲批。<br />\n<br />\n控方曾於早前提堂時指，案發當天有另外三名男子在首被告開設的車房損毀車輛後離去，但他們逃跑時留下死者在現場。三名被告毆打死者並將他制服，其間死者表示不能呼吸，惟沒人鬆手，亦有人再拳打死者。警方到場後，死者已沒脈搏或呼吸，兩小時後證實死亡。首被告在警誡下保持緘默，其餘兩被告則承認曾將死者按在地上。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：STCC4603/18】<br />\n記者羅日昇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190308/59343642\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190308%2F59343642&d=%2BySIvleuZbSdMWEfOjMUQmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=a196427a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190308%2F59343642&h=f5c3b6e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190308/59343642</a>"},{"pid":"5b741e0ae3aea0e90af3efd05521ac109b71cb63","tid":1051973,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:06:19.000Z","msg":"警黑合作無間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ead6b3381e6a6f9bd10b87bad4461ac977cae7f","tid":1051973,"uid":39948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:09:53.000Z","msg":"呢單野咩料，律政司做錯野？"},{"pid":"38c14d88d6b1d254be1944d5b0c9f37322d26914","tid":1051973,"uid":136186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:10:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DSs8Prs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDSs8Prs.png&h=40959da6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c01ad18a1465fb87498d35379fb336d411f7839","tid":1051973,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:11:53.000Z","msg":"律政司放生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ab49a4c9bc8a24201175c9f970884b205eb18d","tid":1051973,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b741e0ae3aea0e90af3efd05521ac109b71cb63","tid":1051973,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:06:19.000Z","msg":"警黑合作無間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:12:00.000Z","msg":"梁福元<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f4bc77daa87a02359f60a2a0632649e5562b97d","tid":1051973,"uid":50253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b741e0ae3aea0e90af3efd05521ac109b71cb63","tid":1051973,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:06:19.000Z","msg":"警黑合作無間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:14:00.000Z","msg":"好似唔關警察事"},{"pid":"4c4052c9b357a9667c8a272283cf93d9b1b0b09